text: NEW: Rapper Lil Wayne meets with Pres. Donald Trump on the administration's proposed plan for Black America: "He listened to what we had to say today and assured he will and can get it done." https://t.co/uDK1okg0d7

name: ABC
text: NEW: The U.S. has set a new single-day record for cases, according to The COVID Tracking Project. There were 88,452 cases reported on Thursday, well above the seven-day average of 76,302. The U.S. also tested 1.3 million people. https://t.co/oCyI3jtNHP

name: ABC
text: More than 1.7 million customers are still without power across Louisiana, Mississippi, Alabama, Georgia and the Carolinas. https://t.co/8cYcr2Ulgj

name: ABC
text: Hospital staff, cheerleaders, friends, family and classmates lined the streets to welcome home Sarah Frei, 17, who underwent 20 surgeries after a crash, in which the car she was riding in with three friends was hit head-on by an alleged drunk driver. https://t.co/KWhgXLs9f7
